trans-unit.source: Specifies whether a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel"></xref> object on a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar"></xref> control is owner-drawn or system-drawn.
trans-unit.target: Anger om en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel"> </xref> objekt på en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar"> </xref> kontrollen är ägare ritas eller system ritas.

trans-unit.source: Use the members of this enumeration to set the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel.Style%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> class.
trans-unit.target: Använd medlemmarna i den här uppräkningen för att ange värdet på <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel.Style%2A>egenskapen för <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>klassen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel.Style%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Style property determines the way in which the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> will be displayed.
<xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> objects can display simple text or be owner-drawn.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>objekt kan visa enkel text eller vara ägare ritas.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>

trans-unit.source: Owner-drawn <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> objects support displaying images or a different font from the rest of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> objects on a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar> control, while system-drawn <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> objects are used to display only text (or text and an icon if an icon is specified in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel.Icon%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>).
trans-unit.target: Ägare ritas <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>objekt stöd för visning av bilder eller ett annat teckensnitt från resten av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>objekt på en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar>kontroll, medan systemet ritas <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>objekt används för att visa endast text (eller text och ikon om en ikon som anges i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel.Icon%2A>egenskapen för den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>).</xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel.Icon%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>

trans-unit.source: To perform the owner-draw operations on an owner-drawn <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>, use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar.DrawItem> event of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar> control.
trans-unit.target: Utföra åtgärder på en ägare ritats användardefinierad <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>, använda den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar.DrawItem>händelsen för den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar.DrawItem> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel"></xref> is drawn by the owner.
The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel"></xref> displays text in the standard font.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusBarPanel"> </xref> visas texten i standard teckensnitt.
